title: Queensland woman killed by falling tree branch was feeding her horses moments earlier - as husband makes heartbreaking tribute
description: Heartbroken Queensland man, Colin Greenwood, has shared a touching tribute to his wife, Joy, who was killed on Friday after a tree fell on her during a severe storm in Lockyer Waters.

title: Richard Marles' $350 breakfast and laundry bill is exposed after he was blasted for being out of touch with the cost-of-living crisis in Australia
description: Deputy Prime Minister Richard Marles has been revealed to have charged Aussie taxpayers over $350 for breakfast and laundry while in the United States.

title: Handyman and Home Improvement star Bob Vila lists his Florida waterfront mansion for sale with a $59.2 million asking price
description: Bob Vila, 77, and his wife Diana Barrett have listed their Florida mansion for $59.2million. The 6,300 square foot home has seven bedrooms and has beautiful waterfront views.

title: Call the midwives' builder... their church is crumbling! Baroque backdrop to show launches £7m appeal for desperately needed restoration
description: Rainwater damage, cracked plasterwork and collapsing ceilings have left the East End church in Limehouse in desperate need of repair and on Historic England's heritage at-risk register.

title: Suella Braverman was right about biased, woke policing. I should know - I'm an officer on the front line
description: It was the same with Black Lives Matter protests and, for a long time, the hugely disruptive stunts by groups such as Just Stop Oil, bottom left.

title: Nigel Farage set to launch legal battle with NatWest Group and its former boss Dame Alison Rose to seek millions in damages over the debanking scandal
description: Mr Farage is seeking millions in compensation for reputation damage after former NatWest boss Dame Alison Rose admitted to discussing his banking arrangements with the BBC

title: Snowflakes! Woke Wisconsin council sparks outrage after instructing staff to avoid red and green decorations in public buildings and replacing religious ornaments with 'snow people'
description: A Wisconsin city council has issued guidelines to its employees, advising against the use of red and green decorations in public spaces during the Christmas holidays.

title: One giant slip for womankind! Nasa astronauts on a rare all-female space walk drop their toolbox (and experts say it's visible from Earth)
description: The satchel-sized bag was dropped by astronauts as they carried out external maintenance work on the International Space Station (ISS) earlier this month.

title: Police launch probe as Jewish families leaving north London synagogue are 'targeted' by pro-Palestinian activists spraying green smoke and shouting from cars after Armistice Day march
description: Footage shared on Twitter on Saturday night showed men holding green flares, waving Palestine flags and shouting from cars on Abbey Road in St John's Wood, north London.

title: Danny Abdallah recalls heartbreaking moment he came face to face with killer driver Samuel Davidson
description: Danny Abdallah has revealed the moment he came face to face with the killer of three of his children, who died when the driver mowed them down in Sydney's west on February 1, 2020.

title: Netflocks! Now will it be Fiona: The Movie
description: It was the astonishing story that captured the hearts of the nation. Now the daring rescue of Britain's loneliest sheep could be celebrated on screen.

title: The great pub grab! Villagers make legal history in bid to buy their beloved local
description: Villagers are using Scotland's controversial land reform laws in a ground-breaking attempt to take control of their local pub. The Albert Hotel in North Queensferry has been closed since 2017.

title: It's condition critical… and we ALL know the SNP is to blame, writes Dr SANDESH GULHANE, Scots Tory health spokesman
description: It is now clear that the SNP's plans for National Treatment Centres have run into serious delays and problems with their introduction. Many health board are only just at the beginning of the process.

title: SNP's bonfire of their OWN promises
description: New hospitals, roads and railway projects promised by the SNP are under threat as Ministers admit that they are running out of cash.

title: Now SNP asks would-be MPs if they'd back a secret election pact with Labour
description: Fears the SNP could help hand Sir Keir Starmer the keys to No 10 deepened last night amid claims would-be Nationalist MPs are being asked if they would prop up a minority Labour government.

title: As he jets off to the jungle... Nigel Farage is a huge Celebrity on TikTok? Get out of here!
description: The former Brexit Party leader, 59, has become a TikTok sensation with his videos on topics such as smoking legislation, transgender rights and immigration racking up millions of likes
